headlines.description: — Ja Morant had 26 points, 14 assists and 10 rebounds and helped the Memphis Grizzlies build a 31-point second-half cushion and beat the Milwaukee Bucks 122-99 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Morant's triple-double helps Grizzlies build big lead and coast to 122-99 victory over Bucks

headlines.description: — Jalen Green had 23 points and 12 rebounds, Alperen Sengun added 17 points and 12 rebounds, and the Houston Rockets held off a fourth-quarter Dallas rally to beat the Mavericks 108-102 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jalen Green, Alperen Sengun help Rockets hold off late Mavericks rally to win 108-102

events.name: San Antonio Spurs at Utah Jazz

headlines.description: — Victor Wembanyama had 25 points and nine rebounds to lead the San Antonio Spurs to a 106-88 victory over the Utah Jazz on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Wembanyama has 25 points and nine rebounds to lead Spurs to 106-88 win over Jazz

headlines.description: — Devin Booker scored 40 points, Kevin Durant added 18, and the Phoenix Suns rallied from a 21-point deficit to beat the Los Angeles Clippers 125-119 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Booker and Durant lead Suns to 125-1119 comeback win over Clippers
